data.description: Welcome to this charming 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home nestled in Charlotte minutes from the South Carolina border! Enjoy the spacious yard featuring a deck and enclosed porch. Plenty of kitchen cabinets for all your storage needs. Never worry about space when entertaining guests with not only a formal dining room, but a sitting room, family room and breakfast area. Enjoy a two car garage with its own HVAC system for all home year round needs. It would make a wonderful workshop area! Don't miss the opportunity to make this delightful house your home. Schedule a showing today and discover the perfect blend of comfort and style in this Charlotte gem.
